flowchart LR
    SCAN[Finding produced] --> Q{Legitimate content?}
    Q -->|No| REPORT[Report finding]
    Q -->|Yes| SUPP["Add inline suppression\n# bawbel-ignore: rule-id reason"]
    SUPP --> AUDIT[Stored in suppressed_findings\nfor audit trail]
    AUDIT --> EXPIRY{Expiry date set?}
    EXPIRY -->|Yes| EXPIRE[CI fails when expired]
    EXPIRY -->|No| PERMANENT[Permanent suppression]
    style REPORT fill:#7a1a1a,color:#fff
    style EXPIRE fill:#4a2a1a,color:#fff
